288
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:27,640
You were never this fierce before.

289
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:30,750
I didn't recognise you

290
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,790
when you yelled at me today.

291
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:36,640
You looked

292
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:39,830
a lot like a bad guy.

293
00:32:45,110 --> 00:32:46,440
Do you think

294
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:50,400
so now?

295
00:32:55,750 --> 00:32:57,200
I'm sorry.

296
00:32:58,270 --> 00:32:59,310
From now on,

297
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:01,070
I won't yell at you anymore.

298
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,880
You can't yell at Mom either.

299
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:04,640
No more yelling.

300
00:33:06,510 --> 00:33:08,350
Will you play the game with me?

301
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:11,550
I'll play any game you want with you.

302
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,830
Come on, I'll carry you.

303
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,240
Come on.

