00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:34,260
(Xinqiao Inn)

305
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:39,190
Come on.

306
00:33:45,410 --> 00:33:47,350
Why did you run out
in the middle of the night?

307
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,030
It's all my fault.

308
00:33:50,190 --> 00:33:51,680
Let's talk about it when we get back.

309
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:53,270
Let's go.

310
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:09,840
Yan,

311
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:12,760
go back to bed.

312
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,190
I'll talk

313
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:16,190
