355
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:57,840
I have no idea when he's going
to have a slow onset of the illness.

356
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:05,280
It could be years from now.

357
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:09,800
It could be tomorrow.

358
00:37:18,670 --> 00:37:19,960
In your words,

359
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,920
I've been too selfish before.

360
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:29,800
From now on, I just want

361
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:31,760
the two of us

362
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:33,960
to spend every day with Yan.

363
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:44,670
