372
00:38:23,190 --> 00:38:24,360
Wang Hongyu

373
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,880
helped me get students

374
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,480
because I knew he was smuggling.

375
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:33,030
Do you remember

376
00:38:33,670 --> 00:38:35,440
my classmate, Dong Binghui?

377
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,480
He told me about it.

378
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:41,190
You wouldn't believe me if I told you.

379
00:38:43,710 --> 00:38:44,710
I had

380
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,550
to blackmail him with this

381
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,920
to get you fired.

382
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:49,840
I did it

383
00:38:50,070 --> 00:38:51,630
to protect you.

384
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:07,710
Whatever I have to do for this family,

385
00:39:10,150 --> 00:39:11,550
I'll do it.

386
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:40,360
Gou,

387
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,030
he's here.

388
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:47,710
She's Gou.

389
00:39:48,452 --> 00:39:49,892
She has what you want.

390
00:40:02,370 --> 00:40:04,500
Her man left it behind
when he went to the mountains.

391
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:15,880
Come here.

392
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,480
